Title: Doesn't Hold Water
Description:
Would you mind checking in on Mudmug? He may need some assistance bringing that water back.

I'm sure he'll appreciate the help of a big, strong $c like yourself to help him shoulder the load.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Mudmug at the Gilded Fan in the Valley of the Four Winds.
RewardText: $n! You here to help out? That's mighty swell of you.
